Ek niteliğin doldurulması gerekir olup olmadığını gösterir.

Shows whether the attribute inherits the list of values from a master attribute.
Ten atrybut używa listy wartości atrybutu wzorcowego.
El atributo utiliza la lista de valores de muestra de atributos.
Реквизит может быть в нескольких разных наборах.
Shows whether the attribute can be included in multiple attribute sets.
Dane mogą występować w kilku różnych zestawach.
Attribute können in mehreren verschiedenen Mengen vorliegen.
Atributul poate face parte din mai multe seturi diferite.
El atributo puede aparecer en varios conjuntos diferentes.

Settings.QueryText: SELECT Sets.Ref AS Ref, Sets.DataVersion AS DataVersion, Sets.DeletionMark AS DeletionMark, Sets.Predefined AS Predefined, Sets.Parent AS Parent, Sets.IsFolder AS IsFolder, Sets.Description AS Description, Sets.Used AS Used, CASE WHEN Sets.IsFolder THEN PRESENTATION(Sets.Ref) WHEN &IsAdditionalInfoSets THEN CASE WHEN Sets.InfoCount = "" THEN PRESENTATION(Sets.Ref) WHEN Sets.InfoCount <> "" AND &IsMainLanguage THEN Sets.Description + " (" + Sets.InfoCount + ")" ELSE (CAST(ISNULL(PresentationSets.Description, Sets.Description) AS STRING(150))) + " (" + Sets.InfoCount + ")" END ELSE CASE WHEN Sets.AttributesCount = "" THEN PRESENTATION(Sets.Ref) WHEN Sets.InfoCount <> "" AND &IsMainLanguage THEN Sets.Description + " (" + Sets.AttributesCount + ")" ELSE (CAST(ISNULL(PresentationSets.Description, Sets.Description) AS STRING(150))) + " (" + Sets.AttributesCount + ")" END END AS Presentation, CASE WHEN Sets.DeletionMark THEN 1 ELSE 0 END + CASE WHEN Sets.Predefined THEN 2 ELSE 0 END AS PictureNumber FROM Catalog.AdditionalAttributesAndInfoSets AS Sets LEFT JOIN Catalog.AdditionalAttributesAndInfoSets.Presentations AS PresentationSets ON (PresentationSets.Ref = Sets.Ref) AND (PresentationSets.LanguageCode = &LanguageCode) WHERE CASE WHEN Sets.Parent = VALUE(Catalog.AdditionalAttributesAndInfoSets.EmptyRef) THEN Sets.Ref IN (&Sets) ELSE Sets.Parent IN (&Sets) END AND Sets.Used AND ISNULL(Sets.Parent.Used, TRUE)
